# RiskBench Suite

A comprehensive toolkit for end-to-end risk-aware benchmarking of autonomous agents.

## Features

- ðŸ” Task specification and execution
- ðŸ“Š Risk metrics calculation and monitoring
- ðŸŒ Interactive web dashboard
- ðŸ³ Docker support
- ðŸ“ˆ Prometheus metrics integration

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install from PyPI
pip install riskbench-suite

# Or with Poetry
poetry add riskbench-suite
```

## Usage

1. Define a task:

```yaml
name: MyTask
description: A sample task
environment:
  type: SeleniumEnv
  config:
    url: https://example.com
success_criteria:
  - type: ElementPresent
    selector: "#success-message"
risk_metrics:
  - type: CVaR
    alpha: 0.9
    threshold: 100.0
```

2. Run the task:

```bash
riskbench run task.yaml
```

3. View results in the dashboard:

```bash
riskbench dashboard
# Open http://localhost:8000
```

